# Drop challenge illustrations here.
#
# Files in this folder are copied to the production bundle by Vite and
# served at `/challenges/<filename>` (same origin as the rest of the app).
# Reference them from `server/data/challenges/ttc-2026.json` via the
# `imageUrl` field, e.g. `"imageUrl": "/challenges/bay.png"`.
#
# Accepted formats: anything `<img>` understands — png, jpg, webp, svg, gif.
